# Client working state — prospect PII, emails, scores, draft copy. Keep local.
# Exceptions (tracked, no PII):
#   - critique.md: per-run eval signal (ratings + skill-edit ideas)
#   - assumptions.md: one-line assumption statements from each skill-run
#   - logs/critique.log.md: critique-skill log
clients/*
!clients/*/
clients/*/*
!clients/*/critique.md
!clients/*/assumptions.md
!clients/*/logs/
clients/*/logs/*
!clients/*/logs/critique.log.md

# Local Claude Code state
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock

# Env
.env
.env.local
*.env

# OS / editor cruft
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.swp
.vscode/
.idea/
